    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Porta-Tower is a roguelike tower defense game where you can pick up and move your towers to better cover the enemies' path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Move Your Towers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A tower's placement is important, so when a position becomes suboptimal, pick it up and move it! How much you want to move them will depend on what type of towers you have. Long-ranged towers can be left alone for longer, while short-ranged towers will need to be moved more frequently to stay in range of enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180950/extras/42dad9a7d5dd3b4a5e81bcfee41257f0.poster.avif?t=1770704602\" width=1000 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180950/extras/42dad9a7d5dd3b4a5e81bcfee41257f0.webm?t=1770704602\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2180950/extras/42dad9a7d5dd3b4a5e81bcfee41257f0.mp4?t=1770704602\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade Your Towers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you've gathered enough crystals, move your tower to the upgrader and upgrade it. Be careful, though, as moving a tower to the upgrader will take it out of the defense until you put it back in position.</p>",
